(21, 'Pinovk Kid Toy Gun Classic Colt 1911 Toy Gun', 'admin', 9, 5, 64, '359,358,360', '361', 'youtube', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uRzEhLm3-hc', 'Kid Toy Gun', '<p style=\"margin-block: 0.75em; line-height: 1.72; color: rgb(50, 52, 57); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">There was the Hubley Ric-O-Shay, and the Mattel Fanner .45 with the Greenie Stick-Em Caps. There was a Thompson and an M3 Grease gun, the latter with hand crank for a realistic sound. The Man From Uncle Gun combined a Walther P.38 with a buttstock, long barrel and scope. There was a foot-long scale likeness of a Winchester Model 94 I glued together like an airplane model. Finally there was that matchless day when I received my first real gun, a bolt-action .410 shotgun, and toys were no more.</p><p style=\"margin-block: 0.75em; line-height: 1.72; color: rgb(50, 52, 57); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">All that was, I guess, preparation for almost 39 years in the gun industry. And, like much else that was shown in those flickering images, anathema to right-thinking members of today\'s academia.</p><div><br></div>', 15.00, 8.00, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'quantity', 1, 1, 0, 500, 'pc', 1, NULL, 0.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, 0.00, NULL, NULL, 0.00, 'amount', 'flat_rate', '0.00', 0, NULL, 0, 'Pinovk Kid Toy Gun', 'There was the Hubley Ric-O-Shay, and the Mattel Fanner .45 with the Greenie Stick-Em Caps. There was a Thompson and an M3 Grease gun, the latter with hand crank for a realistic sound. The Man From Uncle Gun combined a Walther P.38 with a buttstock, long barrel and scope. There was a foot-long scale likeness of a Winchester Model 94 I glued together like an airplane model. Finally there was that matchless day when I received my first real gun, a bolt-action .410 shotgun, and toys were no more.\r\n\r\nAll that was, I guess, preparation for almost 39 years in the gun industry. And, like much else that was shown in those flickering images, anathema to right-thinking members of today\'s academia.', '361', NULL, 'pinovk-kid-toy-gun-classic-colt-1911-toy-gun-iqxdz', 0, 75.00, 0.00, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-02-04 07:12:32', '2021-02-23 02:31:40'),
