size: 1.25em; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: left;\">The German car maker is promising around a 5% cut in CO2 emissions, 7bhp more power and about 15lb ft extra torque. However, it’s thought the redesigned engines have been primarily optimised to reduce exhaust pollutants as much more stringent regulations come in globally over the next decade</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 1500.00, 1000.00, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 200, 'pc', 1, NULL, 0.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, 0.00, NULL, NULL, 0.00, 'amount', 'flat_rate', '0.00', 0, NULL, 0, 'BMW Engine', 'The German car maker is promising around a 5% cut in CO2 emissions, 7bhp more power and about 15lb ft extra torque. However, it’s thought the redesigned engines have been primarily optimised to reduce exhaust pollutants as much more stringent regulations come in globally over the next decade', '525', NULL, 'BMW-unveils-new-generation-engine-DC8vt', 0, 7500.00, 0.00, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-02-05 10:37:11', '2021-02-23 02:31:40'),
