(41, 41, 'Electric Car For Baby or Kids Model Audi R8 Spyder', 'pc', '<ul style=\"color: rgb(104, 108, 111); font-family: Inter, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.14px;\"><li>Suitable for kids of age 3 – 8 years.</li><li>2 in 1. Children Self Drive and Parental RC Control. &nbsp;You child can drive the car himself using the accelerator and the steering wheel. But if your child is very young and he cannot drive himself, then you can use the remote control to drive the car.</li><li>Swing Function</li><li>Accelerator/ Pedal</li><li>Gear Switch For Forward / Reverse</li><li>Horn, Door open/close, Music Player, Lighting</li><li>Battery: 2 x 6V batteries ( 12 Volt Battery )</li><li>Battery Backup: 3 to 4 hours</li><li>Charging Time: 2 hours</li><li>Audi R8 Baby Car Dimensions :</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Car Weight : 22 Kgs</li></ul>', 'en', '2021-02-05 08:03:01', '2021-02-05 08:03:01'),
(42, 42, 'Inflatable Baby Bath Tub', 'pc', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">When a baby has outgrown the infant bathtub, the Buringer Inflated Baby Tub helps to smooth the big tub transition and make the bathing experience better for you and your little one. The textured non-slip surface keeps baby secure, and inflatable padded design creates a comfy and safe environment for baby to splash around. The bathtub deflates and folds easily, making it perfect for home or travel!</p><h5 style=\"position: relative; font-family: &quot;Exo 2&quot;; color: rgb(30, 48, 110); margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; letter-spacing: 0.03em; padding-bottom: 15px;\">Highlights:</h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li>Made of quality, durable European 0.6P PVC standards material (BPA free). Soft and smooth to protect your baby’s skin.</li><li>The slip-resistant surface and inflatable central air cushion keeps the baby safe and prevent from sliding.</li><li>Ideal for traveling. Easy to use and clean, deflates and folds quickly for compact storage.</li><li>Includes convenient storage pocket on the side for storing baby shampoo/soap or toys.</li><li>Suitable for children able to sit upright unaided (6-36 months).</li></ul>', 'en', '2021-02-05 08:08:55', '2021-02-05 08:08:55'),
