(45, 45, 'SHELY Women\'s Floral Print Maxi Dresses', 'pc', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Material: Top -Rayon/spandex jersey fabric; Skirt: Polyester/spandex knit fabric. Soft and stretchy.This dress is Elegant and casual,very soft to touch.Unique style,stretchy and lightweight,make you beautiful,fashionable.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Features: Floral Print,Casual Style,Elegant,Floor Length,simple but fashion style dress，good coverage for casual and formal, Super soft, stretchy and lightweight,elastic in the waist to make a comfortable fit.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">This Women\'s Floral Maxi Dresses is suitable for Party,daily, vacation, work,outdoor, travel.casual, wedding, streetwear, holiday, banquet, vocation, party, also great for pregnant women</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Note:Please be reminded that due to lighting effects and monitor\'s brightness/contrast settings etc, the color tone of the website\'s photo and the actual item could be slightly different.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Size chart is provided. Please allow 1-2cm differs due to manual measurement.Packag