(47, 47, 'NioBe Clothing Women\'s Juniors Rolled Cuffs Ankle Length Distressed Denim Overalls', 'pc', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">69% Cotton, 22% Polyester, 7% Rayon, 1% Spandex</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Machine Wash</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">The coolest throwback style imaginable: NioBe Clothing jean overalls for women has a casual feel that provides a relaxed yet put-together look. Style with sneakers and a printed headband for a weekend-ready look or with a white button-down shirt for casual workdays.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Easy to put on &amp; remove: With two secure button side closures, these denim overalls for women is easy to wear, just like jeans. Besides, this one-and-done outfit eliminates the need to choose pick pants and matching t-shirts which by the way can be very time-consuming.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Five-pocket design: Who doesn’t like pockets? The more the merrier. That is why we have included five functional pockets in our women’s overalls – two large side pockets, two back pockets, and one large chest pocket.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">Distressed look: Distressed patches with whiskers and hand sanding around the legs adds a touch of style to these jeans overalls. Our overall also features a sporty racerback rolled ankle cuffs for an ankle-skimming look. Junior Sizing: 26\" Inseam.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block;\">High-performance fabric: Our women’s overalls are crafted from 69% Cotton, 22% Polyester, 7% Rayon, 1% Spandex for required durability and long-lasting use. Cotton &amp; polyester offers softness while rayon and spandex offer stretchability.</span></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-02-05 09:14:22', '2021-02-05 09:14:22'),
(48, 48, 'Elegant Shrug With Lacework-Not An Abaya', 'pc', '<p style=\"margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 15px;\">\"A chic and elegant piece of every fashionista\'s wardrobe. This classic Shrug embellished with black Lace work on front panels and pockets on both sides will certainly make you feel luxurious as well as classy.<br>Pair it up with any casual dress.</p><p style=\"margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 15px;\">This Garment falls in to \'Modest Wear Category\'\' and It is not a Religious / Islamic Garment. It should be worn in front of Mahrams only.\"</p>', 'en', '2021-02-05 09:23:41', '2021-02-05 09:23:41'),
