(76, 76, 'Apple Pencil', 'pc', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">* COMPATIBLE MODELS *-- Compatible with all iPad series (iPad Pro Air Mini) released after 2018. Compatible models: iPad (6th generation), iPad (7th generation), iPad Air (3rd generation), iPad Mini (5th generation), 11-inch / 12.9-inch iPad Pro, etc. * Note: iPad mini 1/2/3/4 etc. IPad and iPhone / Android / Microsoft devices released before 2018 are not supported.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">* No complicated settings * -One-click operation, no complicated settings, just press the power button of the touch pen. The SUNTAIHO touch pen has a built-in lithium battery, and it takes about 60 minutes to charge from 0 to 100%. Without using the pen, it will automatically shut down after 5 minutes. It also has a magnetic adsorption function, so it is very convenient to carry around in business trips and meetings. (Only iPad Pro (3Gen); iPad Pro 11 inch supports magnetic attraction function)</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">* PALM REJECTION *--Prevent wrong operation. Equipped with a palm rejection function, even if your hand touches the screen, it will not malfunction. When using the touch pen, you can put your hand on the screen freely and write on paper like a pencil. You can naturally focus on work without worrying about anything. This is a very important function for people who perform precise work or long working hours.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">* ULTRA HIGH SENSITIVITY/FINE NIB *--SUNTAIHO touch pen uses POM material to change from thin nib to round nib, which reduces the scratch resistance of the device screen. It is the perfect choice when you want to play a puzzle game without smudging the screen. It is easy to use even in a quiet environment without noise, and is convenient for the touch operation of the game that recognizes the input text by the finger and the operation of the application program.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">International products have separate terms, are sold from abroad and may differ from local products, including fit, age ratings, and language of product, labeling or instructions.</span></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-02-06 07:38:14', '2021-02-06 07:38:14'),
(77, 77, 'IPhone 18W USB-C Charger Power Adapter', 'pc', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">✅MFi CERTIFIED FAST CHARGING &amp; SYNC - ilikable iPhone Charger Cable uses genuine Mfi chip and is made of premium quality tin coated copper wire, which allows you to enjoy max up to 2.4A fast charging speed and 480 Mbps high data transmission anytime.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">✅ ULTRA DURABLE - ilikable iPhone charger cable with reinforced joint design has passed 15,000+ bend tests, extra durable to withstand daily wear and tear. Besides, our iPhone lightning cable adopts professional production technology, ensuring complete safety and reliability.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">✅ EXTRA LONG - Comes with 3 pack 2M premium iPhone charger cable, saving you from a lot of awkward arm positions while your phone is charging. You can use our lightning cable conveniently on the bed, sofa or even in the backseat of car.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">✅ WIDE COMPATIBILITY - ilikable MFi certified lightning cable iPhone charger lightning works seamlessly with any iOS devices with lightning port, including iPhone 12/11/ XS / XR / X / 8 /7 / 6S / 6 / SE 2020 / 5; iPad air/ mini / iPad pro (2017), iPod, airpods and more.</span></li><li style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">✅ WHAT YOU GET - MFi certified lightning cable 2M 3 Pack, and 3 Years warranty and customer service support. If you have